results.title: Metal Wall Art, Words, Live, Laugh, Love, Wall Decor
results.description:
DESCRIPTION
Love Beyond Words can help us through all moments of live!  These beautiful words will look stunning in any location in your house.  In a living room, bedroom,hall or den. 

The piece measures 11" tall by 17" wide, made from 11 gauge aluminum or mild steel and is finished in a textured black powder coat.

This piece is part of a longer saying - check out my other listing if you are interested in purchasing the full set.
https://www.etsy.com/ca/listing/529416038/metal-wall-art-words-live-laugh-love?ref=shop_home_active_1

NOTE: Wood shown behind artwork does not come with the piece, its is a photography backdrop only.

WHICH MATERIAL SHOULD I CHOOSE?
I now offer two material options for your artwork. You can choose between Aluminum or Mild Steel. The finished look of either option is exactly the same, but each type of metal has different characteristics.  Aluminum is lighter and easier to handle and hang. It is also rust proof and therefore the recommended choice for any artwork that is to be hung outside.  Mild steel although susceptible to rust is completely safe for an indoor installation.  Mild steel is heavier which gives the piece a more substantial feel. It is also stronger.
If you have any questions about which option would be best for your application, please send me a message and I can help you make the choice.

SHIPPING
Orders will be shipped via Canada Post, Unites States Parcel Service (USPS), UPS, FedEx or Purolator.  If one of these services does not work for you, please add a note to your order so we can best accommodate your shipping needs.  

US customers –  Most packages will be shipped through Purolator and delivered by UPS.   Packages shipped through Canada Post will be delivered by USPS.
